name: Rocks or cookies - The feats of kalawasa
name_original: Rocks or cookies - The feats of kalawasa
description:
• I'm an owl engraved on a pumpkin, my human made me like this because he likes "mates burilados" a lot, like these.
  • I have been in very curious and incredible places.
  • Anything that looks like a cookie catches my eye.
